data.description: Country living at its finest! This home was built in the mid to late 1800's and has tons of character! Beautiful hardwood floors throughout, Granite counter tops, tiled walk in shower and ample amounts  of storage! The plumbing and electrical was updated in 2004. Roof is only 3 years old and HVAC System installed in December of 2022. Fenced in back yard, nice workshop with a 20x20 basement, 2 carports, 3 old tobacco barns that just need a roof and would make even more storage! Property is located on a quite street that turns into a dirt road so traffic is to a minimum and offers lots of privacy! Don't miss out on this property call today to schedule your private showing!
